  "hotBookmarks": [
    {
      "bookmarkId": "22780717_3_9814-9856",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "9814-9856",
      "markText": "人生中的逆境会以许多不同的方式出现，假如一个人不能掌控自己的命运，他就会被命运掌控。",
      "totalCount": 2873,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=22780717&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=9814&rangeEnd=9856",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/66c32bd0715b9b2d66cf861?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=9814&rangeEnd=9856"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "22780717_14_11444-11489",
      "chapterUid": 14,
      "range": "11444-11489",
      "markText": "在小屋的角落里，有张双人桌。坐在桌旁等着的她，头发虽然已经斑白，身姿却依然像杨柳一样婀娜。",
      "totalCount": 2156,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=22780717&chapterUid=14&rangeStart=11444&rangeEnd=11489",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/66c32bd0715b9b2d66cf861?chapterUid=14&rangeStart=11444&rangeEnd=11489"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "22780717_4_16040-16073",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "16040-16073",
      "markText": "正如伯爵自己在数小时之前所说的：最优秀的狗应该让最老练的人带才对。",
      "totalCount": 2072,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=22780717&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=16040&rangeEnd=16073",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/66c32bd0715b9b2d66cf861?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=16040&rangeEnd=16073"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "22780717_3_100104-100199",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "100104-100199",
      "markText": "因为从现在开始，不用四年，他，亚历山大·伊里奇·罗斯托夫，在再次听完双响座钟的十二声钟鸣之后，将会穿上他心爱的外套，爬上大都会酒店的屋顶，然后坚定地走向屋顶边的栏杆，好纵身朝下面的街道跃去。",
      "totalCount": 1820,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=22780717&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=100104&rangeEnd=100199",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/66c32bd0715b9b2d66cf861?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=100104&rangeEnd=100199"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "22780717_9_18007-18058",
      "chapterUid": 9,
      "range": "18007-18058",
      "markText": "“谁又能想到，”他说，“许多年前，当你被判在大都会酒店终身监禁的时候，你其实成了全俄罗斯最幸运的人。”",
      "totalCount": 1599,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=22780717&chapterUid=9&rangeStart=18007&rangeEnd=18058",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/66c32bd0715b9b2d66cf861?chapterUid=9&rangeStart=18007&rangeEnd=18058"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "22780717_3_6083-6137",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "6083-6137",
      "markText": "可有一种经验却是我们不太能学到的，那便是：如何与最心爱的东西告别。即使有学习的机会，我们也宁可对之退避三舍。",
      "totalCount": 1560,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=22780717&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=6083&rangeEnd=6137",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/66c32bd0715b9b2d66cf861?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=6083&rangeEnd=6137"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "22780717_3_99174-99215",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "99174-99215",
      "markText": "躺在这只温馨的小盒子里的正是尼娜的那把酒店的万能钥匙，上面还拴着一根深绿色的缎带。",
      "totalCount": 1518,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=22780717&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=99174&rangeEnd=99215",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/66c32bd0715b9b2d66cf861?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=99174&rangeEnd=99215"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "22780717_4_13432-13532",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "13432-13532",
      "markText": "人类生来就有变化无常的天性，他们是如此复杂又如此令人着迷的矛盾体。对他们，我们不仅需要去认真思考，而且得再三地思考。在利用尽可能多的场合和机会同他们充分接触之前，我们断然不要对他们中的任何人抱有成见。",
      "totalCount": 1496,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=22780717&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=13432&rangeEnd=13532",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/66c32bd0715b9b2d66cf861?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=13432&rangeEnd=13532"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "22780717_3_3994-4023",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "3994-4023",
      "markText": "“国王用城堡使自己强大，”伯爵在一旁说，“绅士则用书桌。”",
      "totalCount": 1394,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=22780717&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=3994&rangeEnd=4023",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/66c32bd0715b9b2d66cf861?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=3994&rangeEnd=4023"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "22780717_3_65057-65132",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "65057-65132",
      "markText": "“所有的小女孩长大之后，都不会再对公主之类的事情感兴趣了，”她说，“事实上，当她们对公主已经不再感兴趣的时候，有些小男孩对满世界乱爬的兴趣还浓着呢。”",
      "totalCount": 1350,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=22780717&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=65057&rangeEnd=65132",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/66c32bd0715b9b2d66cf861?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=65057&rangeEnd=65132"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "22780717_6_10259-10286",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "10259-10286",
      "markText": "所以说，是的，生活一直都在滚滚向前，一如既往地行进着。",
      "totalCount": 1241,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=22780717&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=10259&rangeEnd=10286",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/66c32bd0715b9b2d66cf861?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=10259&rangeEnd=10286"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "22780717_3_11589-11625",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "11589-11625",
      "markText": "不过沉溺于如果情况不同又会发生什么的设想，绝对是让人精神失常的不二法门。",
      "totalCount": 1204,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=22780717&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=11589&rangeEnd=11625",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/66c32bd0715b9b2d66cf861?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=11589&rangeEnd=11625"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "22780717_3_46498-46558",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "46498-46558",
      "markText": "终日无所事事的他拥有大把时间。那种无聊而又倦怠的感觉，陷在泥泞之中无法自拔的可怕之感不断袭上伯爵心头，让他片刻不得安宁。",
      "totalCount": 1122,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=22780717&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=46498&rangeEnd=46558",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/66c32bd0715b9b2d66cf861?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=46498&rangeEnd=46558"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "22780717_3_83787-83843",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "83787-83843",
      "markText": "从大钟变成枪炮，又从枪炮再变回大钟，从眼下再到时光的尽头，就这么一直循环反复地变下去。而这就是铁矿石永恒的命运。",
      "totalCount": 1056,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=22780717&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=83787&rangeEnd=83843",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/66c32bd0715b9b2d66cf861?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=83787&rangeEnd=83843"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "22780717_3_22912-22967",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "22912-22967",
      "markText": "悲伤这种情绪最好是拿来与众人分担。 或者自己独自面对。",
      "totalCount": 1022,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=22780717&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=22912&rangeEnd=22967",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/66c32bd0715b9b2d66cf861?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=22912&rangeEnd=22967"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "22780717_3_31350-31407",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "31350-31407",
      "markText": "这样下去，要不了多久，他便能感觉到天花板正往下压，墙壁正往里挤，地板正往上抬，整个酒店慢慢被压成了饼干盒一般大小。",
      "totalCount": 1022,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=22780717&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=31350&rangeEnd=31407",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/66c32bd0715b9b2d66cf861?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=31350&rangeEnd=31407"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "22780717_13_10251-10313",
      "chapterUid": 13,
      "range": "10251-10313",
      "markText": "因为在生活中，真正重要的并不是我们能否获得一轮又一轮的喝彩声，而是在面对这种荣誉的不确定性时，我们是否仍然敢于鼓起勇气前进。",
      "totalCount": 1005,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=22780717&chapterUid=13&rangeStart=10251&rangeEnd=10313",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/66c32bd0715b9b2d66cf861?chapterUid=13&rangeStart=10251&rangeEnd=10313"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "22780717_3_14129-14141",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "14129-14141",
      "markText": "生活中的诱惑毕竟太多了。",
      "totalCount": 976,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=22780717&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=14129&rangeEnd=14141",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/66c32bd0715b9b2d66cf861?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=14129&rangeEnd=14141"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "22780717_7_20191-20255",
      "chapterUid": 7,
      "range": "20191-20255",
      "markText": "“那你就该相信她。即便现在她一心奔着错误的方向去，你也要相信，她迟早会找到她生命的归宿。因为我们每个人迟早都会找到自己的归宿。”",
      "totalCount": 972,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=22780717&chapterUid=7&rangeStart=20191&rangeEnd=20255",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/66c32bd0715b9b2d66cf861?chapterUid=7&rangeStart=20191&rangeEnd=20255"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "22780717_3_73394-73467",
